<h1> Pro Tip</h1>
<div id="pro-tip" style="background-color: #f1f1f1;">
	<br>
	Find Files with Grep:

	<p>
	<code>
		grep -rl . -e PATTERN
	</code>
	</p>

	<p>
		Grep will search each file from "here" downwards,
		and, if the contents of that file match PATTERN,
		print the name of the file.
	</p>

	Option Summary:
	<ul style="list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0">
		<li><code>-r</code> Recursively descend through directory tree </li>
		<li><code>-l</code> List files; do not print matching line </li>
		<li><code>.</code> Begin at current directory </li>
		<li><code>-e</code>   What follows is a PATTERN
		</li>
	</ul>
	<br>

</div>
